        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 40px;">
            We are a passionate team of developers, designers, and innovators dedicated to building high-quality
            web and mobile applications that make life easier and businesses smarter.
        </p>

        <!-- Cards -->
        <div class="row" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; justify-content: center;">

            <div class="card" style="flex: 1 1 300px; background: #fff; border-radius: 15px; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                <h3 style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px;">Our Mission</h3>
                <p style="color: #666;">
                    To deliver innovative and scalable software solutions that empower businesses and connect people globally.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card" style="flex: 1 1 300px; background: #fff; border-radius: 15px; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                <h3 style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px;">Our Vision</h3>
                <p style="color: #666;">
                    To become a leading technology partner worldwide by creating meaningful digital experiences.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card" style="flex: 1 1 300px; background: #fff; border-radius: 15px; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                <h3 style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px;">Our Values</h3>
                <p style="color: #666;">
                    Integrity, innovation, and excellence drive everything we do for our clients and community.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Section -->
        <div style="margin-top: 60px;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 30px;">Meet Our Team</h2>
